      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth driving experience and plenty of comfort for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It's a solid, dependable choice that\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner!",
