    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips expected from regular driving. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as they should. It drives smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
